00:19:16,683 --> 00:19:18,318
The Blue King foolishly
thinks he can suppress

288
00:19:18,351 --> 00:19:21,187
the Slate's power, just
as the Gold King did.

289
00:19:22,455 --> 00:19:24,457
So I was just going to
wait until that rookie

290
00:19:24,490 --> 00:19:28,294
exhausted himself. That
was my original plan.

291
00:19:29,162 --> 00:19:30,964
But this calls for a change.

292
00:19:32,065 --> 00:19:34,200
Now that I've come
back you won't be able

293
00:19:34,234 --> 00:19:35,569
to do as you please.

294
00:19:36,469 --> 00:19:37,470
I see...

295
00:19:38,639 --> 00:19:41,341
I wanted to partner with you
and move the world forward.

296
00:19:42,208 --> 00:19:46,713
However, if instead you wish
to choose confrontation...

297
00:19:47,748 --> 00:19:49,415
I'm happy to oblige.

298
00:19:55,188 --> 00:19:57,490
There's one other thing I
want to confirm with you.

299
00:19:58,091 --> 00:19:59,392
The incident last year...

300
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:02,035
Is it safe for me to
assume that you were the

