00:20:02,102 --> 00:20:06,272
one who dragged me
into this little game?

302
00:20:10,043 --> 00:20:12,345
Oh, so you figured
it out, huh?

303
00:20:13,046 --> 00:20:16,349
This body I'm in, not even
the Blue Clan's Yuishiki

304
